<item>
            <title>[LU-2305] Test failure sanityn, test_16: fsx bus error, core dumped</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2305</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e9d17d32-d077-11e1-9002-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e9d17d32-d077-11e1-9002-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_16 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;== sanityn test 16: 2500 iterations of dual-mount fsx  07:13:29 (1342534409)&lt;br/&gt;
Chance of close/open is 1 in 50&lt;br/&gt;
Seed set to 4410&lt;br/&gt;
fd 0: /mnt/lustre/fsxfile&lt;br/&gt;
fd 1: /mnt/lustre2/fsxfile&lt;br/&gt;
/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanityn.sh: line 330: 23967 Bus error               fsx -c 50 -p 100 -N 2500 -l $((SIZE * 256)) -S 0 $MOUNT1/fsxfile $MOUNT2/fsxfile&lt;br/&gt;
 sanityn test_16: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_16 failed with 135 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are no messages on the client or OST console logs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanityn 16&lt;/p&gt;</description>
